Package: QuasarExperiment
Title: SummarizedExperiment Interface for the quasar eQTL Mapping Tool
Version: 0.1.3
Authors@R: c(
    person("Vincent", "Carey", email = "stvjc@channing.harvard.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Claude", "Sonnet", role = "eng",
           comment = "Anthropic AI assistant"))
Description: Provides a SummarizedExperiment-derived container,
    QuasarExperiment, for managing phenotype, covariate, genotype, and
    genetic relatedness matrix data for use with the quasar eQTL mapping
    tool. Genotype data is represented lazily via BEDMatrix, avoiding
    loading large PLINK binary files into memory. A runQuasar() method
    handles file I/O and invokes the quasar binary, returning results as
    GRanges objects.
License: Artistic-2.0
SystemRequirements: quasar eQTL mapping tool (https://github.com/jeffreypullin/quasar);
    a macOS ARM64 binary is bundled in inst/mac_arm_bin
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
biocViews: GeneExpression, SNP, GenomeWideAssociation, Sequencing,
    RNASeq, DataRepresentation
Depends:
    R (>= 4.3.0),
    SummarizedExperiment,
    GenomicRanges
Imports:
    methods,
    utils,
    stats,
    S4Vectors,
    IRanges,
    Matrix,
    BEDMatrix
Suggests:
    BiocStyle,
    knitr,
